    and @Syni{dependent_}@nt{expression}s are known on entry.]}

  @begin{Discussion}
    @ChgRef{Version=[5],Kind=[AddedNormal]}
    @ChgAdded{Version=[5],Text=[It's OK if such an expression raises an
